<subSubSection id="B3EDACB6FFACFF8BFF32FA36FB6B9DE5" pageId="2" pageNumber="522" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="FB48FF3DFFACFF8BFF32FA36FB6B9DE5" blockId="2.[151,1437,150,717]" pageId="2" pageNumber="522">
<emphasis id="C983232FFFACFF8BFF32FA36FEEB9D49" bold="true" box="[199,315,583,609]" pageId="2" pageNumber="522">Remarks.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="3CF784BEFFACFF8BFEB2FA36FE3F9D49" authorityName="MacGillivray" authorityYear="1921" box="[327,495,583,609]" class="Insecta" family="Diaspididae" genus="Unachionaspis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="522" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="C983232FFFACFF8BFEB2FA36FE3F9D49" box="[327,495,583,609]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="522">Unachionaspis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
comprises a predominantly northeastern-Asiatic group of graminivorous species occurring mainly on bamboos. The genus is similar to 
<taxonomicName id="3CF784BEFFACFF8BFCE6FA1AFBAE9DAD" authority="MacGillivray 1921" authorityName="MacGillivray" authorityYear="1921" box="[787,1150,619,645]" class="Insecta" family="Diaspididae" genus="Kuwanaspis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="522" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="C983232FFFACFF8BFCE6FA1AFC4C9DAC" box="[787,924,619,644]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="522">Kuwanaspis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="9F6682CCFFACFF8BFC53FA1AFBAE9DAD" author="MacGillivray, A. D." box="[934,1150,619,645]" pageId="2" pageNumber="522" refId="ref4946" refString="MacGillivray, A. D. (1921) The Coccidae. Tables for the identification of the subfamilies and some of the more important genera and species, together with discussions. Scarab, Urbana, Illinois, 502 pp. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 29515" type="book" year="1921">MacGillivray 1921</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="3CF784BEFFACFF8BFB4FFA1AFF1F9D81" authority="Kuwana 1928" authorityName="Kuwana" authorityYear="1928" class="Insecta" family="Diaspididae" genus="Nikkoaspis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="522" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="C983232FFFACFF8BFB4FFA1AFAE59DAD" box="[1210,1333,619,645]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="522">Nikkoaspis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="9F6682CCFFACFF8BFACAFA1AFF1F9D81" author="Kuwana, S. I." pageId="2" pageNumber="522" pagination="1 - 39" refId="ref4802" refString="Kuwana, S. I. (1928) The diaspine Coccidae of Japan. V. Genera Chionaspis, Tsukushiaspis [n. gen.], Leucaspis, Nikkoaspis [n. gen.]. Scientific Bulletin, Japan, 1, 1 - 39." type="journal article" year="1928">
Kuwana 
<quantity id="3C0F52D8FFACFF8BFF62FAFEFF1F9D81" box="[151,207,655,681]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.897119999999999" pageId="2" pageNumber="522" unit="in" value="1928.0">1928</quantity>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
in the characteristics of the pygidial lobes and the distribution of dorsal macroducts; however, unlike members of 
<emphasis id="C983232FFFACFF8BFF43FAC2FEB49DE5" box="[182,356,691,717]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="522">
<taxonomicName id="3CF784BEFFACFF8BFF43FAC2FEB19DE5" authorityName="MacGillivray" authorityYear="1921" box="[182,353,691,717]" class="Insecta" family="Diaspididae" genus="Unachionaspis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="522" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Unachionaspis</taxonomicName>
,
</emphasis>
species of 
<taxonomicName id="3CF784BEFFACFF8BFE17FAC2FDBB9DE4" authorityName="MacGillivray" authorityYear="1921" box="[482,619,691,716]" class="Insecta" family="Diaspididae" genus="Kuwanaspis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="522" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="C983232FFFACFF8BFE17FAC2FDBB9DE4" box="[482,619,691,716]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="522">Kuwanaspis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="3CF784BEFFACFF8BFD54FAC2FCCC9DE5" authorityName="Kuwana" authorityYear="1928" box="[673,796,691,717]" class="Insecta" family="Diaspididae" genus="Nikkoaspis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="522" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="C983232FFFACFF8BFD54FAC2FCCC9DE5" box="[673,796,691,717]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="522">Nikkoaspis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
possess pygidial plates on each side.
</paragraph>
